commit.message:
Default argument to default_bar_logger() is "bar" not "bars"

https://github.com/Edinburgh-Genome-Foundry/Proglog/blob/master/proglog/proglog.py#L380 shows that you should pass "bar" to default_bar_logger(), not "bars".
